description: Deep-South Resources Inc., a development stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties. It primarily explores for copper deposits. The company holds a 100% interest in the Haib project located in the south of Namibia. The company was formerly known as Jet Gold Corp. and changed its name to Deep-South Resources Inc. in November 2016. Deep-South Resources Inc. was incorporated in 1987 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
